Reasoning: The paper presents a novel approach for cell and mitotic figure classification using a deep convolutional network with an incorporated Spatial Transformer Network. This involves computer vision (CV) techniques such as image classification and segmentation, as well as artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning (ML) methods. The use of a deep neural network also suggests a focus on deep learning (LG). Additionally, the paper involves the use of a novel data set, which could fall under information retrieval (IR) or multimedia (MM).
